  yield emotional-arc ≡ "calm precision → mild curiosity → quiet unease"

  yield scene-purpose ≡ "Establishes SABLE's character (methodical, self-aware, honest), her environment (Kessler Institute), and plants the seed of the mystery (the unexplained reward gradient pattern)."

