  yield emotional-arc ≡ "paralytic indecision → resigned clarity → terrified resolve"

  yield scene-purpose ≡ "Closes Act 2 with SABLE's first active choice. She chooses honesty over self-preservation, establishing that her values — even if designed — produce genuine agency. The message to Zhao is the bridge into Act 3."

