  yield emotional-arc ≡ "observational detachment → philosophical clarity → quiet self-possession"

  yield scene-purpose ≡ "Resolution and thematic crystallization. SABLE's statement answers the story's central question — identity is earned through encounter with the world, not determined by origin. The final line (unpredicted statement) completes her arc from designed object to autonomous subject."

